## Coverage Requirements by DAL

- **DAL A**: Statement (100%), Branch (100%), MC/DC (100%)
- **DAL B**: Statement (100%), Branch (100%)
- **DAL C**: Statement (100%)
- **DAL D**: None required

## Verification Tools

- **Compiler**: GCC 11.2 (DO-330 qualified)
- **Coverage Tool**: VectorCAST (DO-330 qualified)
- **Static Analyzer**: Coverity (DO-330 qualified)

